text: Fiorano Modenese is a comune in the Province of Modena in the Emilia-Romagna region in Italy. Ferrari's private testing track, the Fiorano Circuit is on the border with Maranello. == Districts == The municipality of Fiorano Modenese has 4 districts: Fiorano Modenese, Spezzano, Ubersetto and Nirano. == References == Category:Settlements in Modena
title: Fiorano Modenese
